name: Seedlip Grove 42
description: Cultivated from a trio of bitter peel, lemon, and blood oranges. A sophisticated, bright, citrus blend of Mediterranean Orange, Lemon, Lemongrass and Ginger with a dry finish. 1 x 23.7 fl oz / 700 ml bottle.

name: Seedlip Spice 94
description: Inspired by the deep woods and the spiced aroma of the forest floor. A warm, aromatic blend of allspice & cardamom with citrus top notes to balance the long bitter finish. 1 x 23.7 fl oz / 700 ml bottle.

name: Seedlip Garden 108
description: Rooted in memories eating fresh peas straight from the pod. A complex, herbal blend of peas & traditional garden herbs including rosemary, thyme & spearmint. 1 x 23.7 fl oz / 700 ml bottle.

name: Seedlip Trio
description: The Seedlip Special Offer Trio is a perfect way to explore the full Seedlip range in the comfort of your own home. Discover the aromatic Spice 94, the fresh & herbal Garden 108 & the citrus Grove 42.

name: The Seedlip Recipe Bundle
description: All three Seedlip expressions and our recently released cocktail book.

name: Non-Alcoholic Cocktail Recipe Book
description: An exclusive collection of Seedlip’s finest cocktails, insight into their ethos, technique and ingredients. Highly illustrated, with recipes from the world’s best bartenders and images by photographer Rob Lawson.
